# Reserva de Spots para um Usuário

### Criação de Reserva
POST http://localhost:3000/users/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": "user123",
    "eventId": "event456",
    "spots": ["spot1", "spot2"],
    "ticket_kind": "full",
    "email": "user@example.com"
}

###

# Resposta Esperada de Sucesso
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json

[
    {
        "spotId": "spot1",
        "ticketKind": "full",
        "email": "user@example.com",
        "userId": "user123",
        "userType": "client",  // ou "staff", dependendo do tipo de usuário
        "gender": "male"       // ou "female", dependendo do gênero do usuário e do evento
    },
    {
        "spotId": "spot2",
        "ticketKind": "full",
        "email": "user@example.com",
        "userId": "user123",
        "userType": "client",  // ou "staff", dependendo do tipo de usuário
        "gender": "male"       // ou "female", dependendo do gênero do usuário e do evento
    }
]

###

# Resposta Esperada de Erro
HTTP/1.1 400 Bad Request
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "Spots spot1, spot2 not found"
}

###

HTTP/1.1 400 Bad Request
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "User already has a reservation for one of the requested spots"
}

###

HTTP/1.1 400 Bad Request
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "The maximum number of spots for this event has been reached"
}